title: Butler pops two home runs in Rays finale vs. Blue Jays
text: Butler pops two home runs in Rays finale vs. Blue Jays OCT 04, 11:42 pm Joey Butler's two jacks helped the Rays finish in style with a win over the playoff-bound Toronto Blue Jays. Sunday marked Butler's first start in over a month.
